data.eml:eml: Checklist of the Free-Living Marine Nematodes of the Iberian Peninsula (north east Atlantic)

This dataset contains the digitized treatments in Plazi based on the original journal article Besteiro, Celia, Ayora, Mario (2017): Checklist of the Free-Living Marine Nematodes of the Iberian Peninsula (north east Atlantic). Zootaxa 4347 (2): 228-254, DOI: https://doi.org/10.11646/zootaxa.4347.2.2
